&lt;DIV&gt;Let's face it, folks. Hardly anyone has learned a thing over the last seven years. The players certainly&amp;nbsp;haven't, and that will be demonstrated with the release of Combine. It's going to be one giant race for bragging rights and server-firsts. The disrespect for old-world content which has plagued EQ for years will be magnified tenfold. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
